{"id":767,"parent_id":702,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":767,"title":"Isaiah 65","subtitle":"","short_title":"Isa.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 65"],[".studySummary",["i","Ancient Israel was rejected for rejecting the Lord—The Lord’s people will rejoice and triumph during the Millennium."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.1","order":"02.24.065.50395"},["b","1"],"I am",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"sought"],"of",["i","them that"],"asked not",["i","for me;"],"I am found of",["i","them that"],"sought me not: I said, Behold me, behold me, unto a nation",["i","that"],"was not called by my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"name"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.2","order":"02.24.065.50396"},["b","2"],"I have spread out my hands all the day unto a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"rebellious"],"people, which walketh in a way",["i","that was"],"not good, after their own thoughts;"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.3","order":"02.24.065.50397"},["b","3"],"A people that provoketh me to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"anger"],"continually to my face; that sacrificeth in gardens, and burneth incense upon altars of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"brick"],";"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.4","order":"02.24.065.50398"},["b","4"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Which remain"],"among the graves, and lodge in the monuments, which eat swine’s flesh, and broth of abominable",["i","things is in"],"their vessels;"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.5","order":"02.24.065.50399"},["b","5"],"Which say, Stand by thyself, come not near to me; for I am",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"holier"],"than thou. These",["i","are"],"a smoke in my nose, a fire that burneth all the day."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.6","order":"02.24.065.50400"},["b","6"],"Behold,",["i","it is"],"written before me: I will not keep silence, but will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"recompense"],", even recompense into their bosom,"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.7","order":"02.24.065.50401"},["b","7"],"Your iniquities, and the iniquities of your fathers together, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", which have burned incense upon the mountains, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"blasphemed"],"me upon the hills: therefore will I measure their former work into their bosom."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.8","order":"02.24.065.50402"},["b","8"],"¶Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", As the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"new wine"],"is found in the cluster, and",["i","one"],"saith, Destroy it not; for a blessing",["i","is"],"in it: so will I do for my servants’ sakes, that I may",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"not"],"destroy them all."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.9","order":"02.24.065.50403"},["b","9"],"And I will bring forth a seed out of Jacob, and out of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Judah"],"an inheritor of my mountains: and mine",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"elect"],"shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"inherit"],"it, and my servants shall dwell there."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.10","order":"02.24.065.50404"},["b","10"],"And Sharon shall be a fold of flocks, and the valley of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"Achor"],"a place for the herds to lie down in, for my people that have sought me."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.11","order":"02.24.065.50405"},["b","11"],"¶But ye",["i","are"],"they that forsake the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", that forget my holy mountain, that prepare a table for that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"troop"],", and that furnish the drink offering unto that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"number"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.12","order":"02.24.065.50406"},["b","12"],"Therefore will I number you to the sword, and ye shall all bow down to the slaughter: because when I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"called"],", ye did not answer; when I spake, ye did not hear; but did evil before mine eyes, and did choose",["i","that"],"wherein I delighted not."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.13","order":"02.24.065.50407"},["b","13"],"Therefore thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],", Behold, my servants shall eat, but ye shall be hungry: behold, my servants shall drink, but ye shall be thirsty: behold, my servants shall rejoice, but ye shall be ashamed:"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.14","order":"02.24.065.50408"},["b","14"],"Behold, my servants shall sing for joy of heart, but ye shall cry for sorrow of heart, and shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"howl"],"for vexation of spirit."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.15","order":"02.24.065.50409"},["b","15"],"And ye shall leave your name for a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"curse"],"unto my chosen: for the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"shall slay thee, and call his servants by another",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"name"],":"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.16","order":"02.24.065.50410"},["b","16"],"That he who",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"blesseth himself"],"in the earth shall bless himself in the God of truth; and he that sweareth in the earth shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"swear"],"by the God of truth; because the former troubles are forgotten, and because they are hid from mine eyes."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.17","order":"02.24.065.50411"},["b","17"],"¶For, behold, I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"create"],"new",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"heavens"],"and a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"new"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_17d"},"earth"],": and the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_17e"},"former"],"shall not be remembered, nor come into mind."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.18","order":"02.24.065.50412"},["b","18"],"But be ye glad and rejoice for ever",["i","in that"],"which I create: for, behold, I create Jerusalem a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"rejoicing"],", and her people a joy."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.19","order":"02.24.065.50413"},["b","19"],"And I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"rejoice"],"in Jerusalem, and joy in my people: and the voice of weeping shall be no more heard in her, nor the voice of crying."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.20","order":"02.24.065.50414"},["b","20"],"There shall be no more thence an infant of days, nor an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"old"],"man that hath not filled his days: for the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"child"],"shall die an hundred years old; but the sinner",["i","being"],"an hundred years old shall be accursed."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.21","order":"02.24.065.50415"},["b","21"],"And they shall build houses, and inhabit",["i","them;"],"and they shall plant vineyards, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"eat"],"the fruit of them."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.22","order":"02.24.065.50416"},["b","22"],"They shall not build, and another inhabit; they shall not plant, and another eat: for as the days of a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"tree"],["i","are"],"the days of my people, and mine elect shall long enjoy the work of their hands."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.23","order":"02.24.065.50417"},["b","23"],"They shall not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"labour"],"in vain, nor bring forth for trouble; for they",["i","are"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"seed"],"of the blessed of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_23c"},"offspring"],"with them."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.24","order":"02.24.065.50418"},["b","24"],"And it shall come to pass, that before they call, I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"answer"],"; and while they are yet speaking, I will hear."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.25","order":"02.24.065.50419"},["b","25"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"wolf"],"and the lamb shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"feed"],"together, and the lion shall eat straw like the bullock: and dust",["i","shall be"],"the serpent’s meat. They shall not",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_25c"},"hurt"],"nor destroy in all my holy mountain, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.1a","order":"02.24.065.50420"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.20"},"Rom. 10:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.1b","order":"02.24.065.50422"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.19"},"Isa. 63:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.2a","order":"02.24.065.50424"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.21"},"Rom. 10:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/1.2"},"2 Ne. 1:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.3a","order":"02.24.065.50426"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/anger"},"TG Anger"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.3b","order":"02.24.065.50428"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/20.25.24-25"},"Ex. 20:25 (24–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.4a","order":"02.24.065.50430"},["b","4a"],["span.small","HEB"],"Who sit."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.5a","order":"02.24.065.50432"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/9.11.10-12"},"Matt. 9:11 (10–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/18.11"},"Luke 18:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/31.16.13-19"},"Alma 31:16 (13–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.6a","order":"02.24.065.50434"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/16.18"},"Jer. 16:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/12.1"},"Mosiah 12:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.10"},"D&C 1:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.7a","order":"02.24.065.50436"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/20.27"},"Ezek. 20:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.8a","order":"02.24.065.50438"},["b","8a"],["span.small","OR"],"grape juice."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.8b","order":"02.24.065.50440"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/18.32.23-32"},"Gen. 18:32 (23–32)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.9a","order":"02.24.065.50442"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.35.35-36"},"Ps. 69:35 (35–36)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.9b","order":"02.24.065.50444"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/election"},"TG Election"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.9c","order":"02.24.065.50446"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/18.9"},"Deut. 18:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.10a","order":"02.24.065.50448"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.15"},"Hosea 2:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.11a","order":"02.24.065.50450"},["b","11a"],["span.small","HEB"],"Gad (an idol of fortune)."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.11b","order":"02.24.065.50452"},["b","11b"],["span.small","HEB"],"Meni (an idol of fate)."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.12a","order":"02.24.065.50454"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.4"},"Isa. 66:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.14a","order":"02.24.065.50456"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.12"},"Matt. 8:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.15a","order":"02.24.065.50458"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/28.37"},"Deut. 28:37"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.15b","order":"02.24.065.50460"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/62.2"},"Isa. 62:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/2.17"},"Rev. 2:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.11.10-11"},"D&C 130:11 (10–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.16a","order":"02.24.065.50462"},["b","16a"],["span.small","IE"],"invokes blessings in his own behalf."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.16b","order":"02.24.065.50464"},["b","16b"],["span.small","IE"],"make covenants through the power of God."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.17a","order":"02.24.065.50466"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-creator"},"TG Jesus Christ, Creator"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.17b","order":"02.24.065.50468"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heaven"},"TG Heaven"],"."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.17c","order":"02.24.065.50470"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-renewal-of"},"TG Earth, Renewal of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/millennium"},"Millennium"],"."],["div",{"id":"17d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.17d","order":"02.24.065.50472"},["b","17d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-destiny-of"},"TG Earth, Destiny of"],"."],["div",{"id":"17e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.17e","order":"02.24.065.50474"},["b","17e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/world-end-of"},"TG World, End of"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.18a","order":"02.24.065.50476"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/35.10"},"Isa. 35:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.19a","order":"02.24.065.50478"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/62.5"},"Isa. 62:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.20a","order":"02.24.065.50480"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/old-age"},"TG Old Age"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.20b","order":"02.24.065.50482"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.30"},"D&C 101:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.21a","order":"02.24.065.50484"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.101"},"D&C 101:101"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.22a","order":"02.24.065.50486"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.30"},"D&C 101:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.23a","order":"02.24.065.50488"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/labor"},"TG Labor"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.23b","order":"02.24.065.50490"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/61.9"},"Isa. 61:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"23c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.23c","order":"02.24.065.50492"},["b","23c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-eternal"},"TG Family, Eternal"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.24a","order":"02.24.065.50494"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/9.26"},"Alma 9:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.25a","order":"02.24.065.50496"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peace"},"TG Peace"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.25b","order":"02.24.065.50498"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/30.12.12-15"},"2 Ne. 30:12 (12–15)"],"."],["div",{"id":"25c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.25c","order":"02.24.065.50500"},["b","25c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/60.18.17-22"},"Isa. 60:18 (17–22)"],"."]]}
